<div class="top-container">
  <div class="banner-content">
      <h1>Meet</h1>
      <p>Scheduling a meeting was never easier, let us do the work!</p>
      <%= image_tag('cartoon-meeting.png') %>
      <button id="banner-button">Sign up!</button>
      <a href="/redirect">dashboard events</a>
      <span><a href=""></a></span>
  </div>
  <div class="bottom-container">
    <h1>So how does it work?</h1>
    <div class="info-1">
     <span>
     <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days fa-5x"></i>
     </span>
     <p>Step 1: Sign up and link your google calendar to our app!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-1">
      <span>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-user-group fa-5x"></i>
      </span>
      <p>Step 2: Create a meeting and add the people who should attend!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-1">
      <span>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-gears fa-5x"></i>
      </span>
      <p>Step 3: Meet will check everyones calendar and calculate for you the availabilities</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-1">
      <span>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check fa-5x"></i>
      </span>
      <p>Step 4: Pick the date you prefer and that's it! you're done! ;)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
